026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epost-graduation%20job%20prospects%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I%20fully%20made%20use%20of%20the%20liberal%20arts%20and%20interdisciplinary%20education.%20I%20was%20involved%20in%20multiple%20student%20organizations%2C%20completed%20four%20internships%20in%20the%20film%20industry%2C%20and%20held%20three%20on-campus%20jobs.%20I%20was%20promoted%20to%20manager%20in%20several%20customer-service%20roles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYet%20since%20graduation%2C%20I%20haven't%20been%20able%20to%20find%20a%20part-time%20job%20while%20living%20at%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225692740a-b30a-413e-bec9-b01c3c8f5c10%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI'm%20living%20with%20my%20parents%20for%20now%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20traditional%20advice%20for%20a%20film%20grad%20is%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoving-from-new-york-to-los-angeles-differences-between-coasts-2020-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emove%20to%20Los%20Angeles%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20work%20your%20way%20up%20from%20the%20bottom.%20However%2C%20the%20film%20industry%20is%20feeling%20the%20strain%20of%20multiple%20strikes%2C%20wildfires%2C%20and%20downsizing.%20Opportunities%20are%20sparse.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELuckily%20for%20me%2C%20I've%20been%20able%20to%20live%20with%20my%20parents%20as%20I%20consider%20where%20and%20when%20to%20take%20a%20full-time%20plunge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20extremely%20grateful%20to%20have%20a%20supportive%20community%20that%20has%20afforded%20me%20the%20time%20to%20review%20my%20prospects.%20As%20I%20consider%20everything%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Funemployed-months-grad-school-middle-age-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egrad%20school%20programs%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20moving%20across%20the%20country%2C%20I'm%20on%20the%20hunt%20for%20a%20part-time%20gig.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20been%20trying%20to%20strike%20a%20balance%20between%20helping%20my%20parents%20financially%2C%20contin