0my%20feet%20were%20still%20wet%20after%20the%20water%20drained%20out%2C%20but%20not%20for%20long%20%E2%80%94%20the%20Climacool%20material%20dries%20quickly.%20About%2015%20minutes%20after%20leaving%20the%20water%2C%20I%20was%20on%20riding%20a%20bike%20on%20a%20trail%20and%20my%20shoes%20and%20feet%20were%20almost%20completely%20dry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20day%2C%20I%20went%20ATVing%20on%20some%20trails%20that%20were%20so%20dusty%20you'd%20be%20a%20fool%20not%20to%20wear%20sunglasses%20and%20a%20bandana%20to%20cover%20your%20face.%20Although%20your%20shoes%20are%20super%20important%20while%20riding%20an%20ATV%2C%20I'd%20say%20that%20a%20normal%20pair%20of%20water%20shoes%2C%20or%20any%20pair%20of%20sneakers%20you%20don't%20want%20to%20be%20ruined%2C%20would%20be%20a%20bad%20choice.%20My%20shoes%20%E2%80%94%20along%20with%20the%20rest%20of%20my%20body%20%E2%80%94%20were%20completely%20covered%20in%20dust%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20excursion.%20Fortunately%2C%20I%20was%20able%20to%20rinse%20my%20shoes%20off%20and%20continue%20to%20wear%20them%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20terms%20of%20fit%2C%20I%20recommend%20going%20true%20to%20size.%20Since%20I%20was%20wearing%20mine%20in%20and%20out%20of%20the%20water%2C%20I%20didn't%20wear%20any%20socks%20%E2%80%94%20and%20I%20would%20imagine%20that's%20how%20Adidas%20intended%20them%20to%20be%20worn.%20If%20for%20some%20reason%20you%20do%20want%20to%20wear%20socks%20with%20them%2C%20you%20should%20still%20have%20room%20when%20you%20wear%20your%20true%20size.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2232b66672-2d63-4b91-9011-13176f8c68d4%5C%22%3EThe%20bottom%20line%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20putting%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20nofollow%20sponsored%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiip_071819_adidas-terrex-parley-water-shoe-20%26h%3Ddcb5c237d6176309d1b11c1cbb2ff23619e67591c1b33e57d0728cf989dc026e%26postID%3D61b8efc7f2a36b1ac9f4265f%26postSlug%3D