%20Clarks'%20sneakers%20and%20I%20was%20very%C2%A0impressed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20taking%20the%20shoes%20out%20of%20the%20box%2C%20the%20first%20thing%20that%20made%20an%20impression%20was%20the%20amazing%20use%20of%20materials.%20My%20favorite%20Clarks%20Original%20silhouette%20is%20the%20Wallabee%20and%20I've%20owned%20both%20leather%20and%20suede%20pairs.%20The%20Trigenic%20Evo%20used%C2%A0both%20tumbled%20leather%20and%20suede%2C%20which%20made%20for%20a%20pair%20of%C2%A0truly%20premium%20sneakers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20my%20experience%2C%20Clarks%20run%20big%2C%20and%20the%20Trigenic%20Evos%20are%20no%20different.%20I%20asked%20for%20a%20pair%20a%20full%20size%20smaller%20than%20the%20one%20I'd%20usually%20get%20for%20sneakers%20and%20got%20a%20perfect%20fit.%C2%A0If%20you%20plan%20to%20wear%20thicker%20than%20normal%20socks%2C%20I'd%20recommend%20going%20down%20a%20half%20size.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAfter%20wearing%20the%20sneakers%20for%20a%20full%20day%2C%20I%20can't%20imagine%20them%C2%A0being%20uncomfortable%20on%20anybody.%20The%20asymmetrical%20design%20forms%20to%20and%20moves%20with%20the%20foot.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20shoes%20crease%20when%20you%20walk%20because%20they%20don't%20move%20with%20the%20natural%20motion%20of%20feet.%20With%20a%20supple%20upper%20and%20three-piece%20outsole%2C%20the%20Trigenic%20Evo%20simply%20flexes%20as%20you%20walk.%20I%20also%20really%20appreciated%20the%20use%20of%20Vibram%20soles%2C%20which%20are%20durable%20and%20long%20lasting.%20That%20choice%20means%20the%20bottoms%20of%20these%20shoes%20will%20last%20just%20as%20long%20as%20the%20premium%20upper.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22sole%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F59a86d0f79bbfd2b008b71bd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22400%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ECountry%20Attire%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EComfort%2C%20quality%2C%20and%20style%20are%20at%20the%