Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ELane%20Eight%20is%20a%20sustainable%20vegan%20sneaker%20startup%20that%20makes%20workout%20shoes%20for%20all%20types%20of%20athletes.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20brand%20uses%20materials%20like%20recycled%20plastic%20and%20algae%20reduce%20impact%20on%20the%20planet.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EWe%20tested%20the%20popular%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noopener%20sponsored%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Flaneeight.com%2Fproduct%2Fmens-trainer-ad-1-cloud-white%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETrainer%20AD1%20sneakers%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20talked%20to%20the%20founder%20about%20the%20shoes.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESneakers%20are%20one%20of%20the%20fastest%20growing%20categories%20in%20the%20apparel%20industry.%20Founded%20in%202017%20by%20Josh%20Shorrock%2C%20Lane%20Eight%20is%20an%20up-and-coming%20sustainable%20and%20vegan%20sneaker%20brand%20that%20uses%20materials%20like%20recycled%20plastic%20water%20bottles%20and%20algae%20to%20make%20its%20performance%20training%20sneakers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt's%20no%20secret%20that%20sustainability%20has%20been%20trending%20upwards%20in%20recent%20years%2C%20with%20big%20brands%20like%20Nike%20and%20Adidas%20taking%20steps%20to%20lighten%20their%20impact%20on%20our%20planet.%20But%20it's%20refreshing%20to%20see%20newer%20startups%20putting%20in%20the%20effort%20from%20day%20one.%20In%20addition%20to%20putting%20the%20planet%20first%20with%20its%20materials%20and%20manufacturing%20techniques%2C%20Lane%20Eight%20also%20aims%20to%20improve%20sustainability%20by%20simply%20making%20shoes%20people%20can%20use%20more%20than%20one%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20point%20of%20differentiation%20is%20our%20focus%20on%20versatility%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Lane%20Eight%20co-founder%20Josh%20Shorrock.%20%26quot%3BWhile%20most%20performance%20brands%20separate%20their%20products%20based%20on%20sport-specific%20categories%20like%20running%20or%20training%2C%20we%20develop%20footwear%20that%20is%20versatile%20and%20responsive%20enough%20to%20handle%20all%20the%20ways%20Everyday%20Athletes%20train%20and%20move%2C%20all%20in%20one%20shoe.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20better%20get%20a%20feel%20for%20the%20brand%2C%20we%20tested%20Lane%20Eight%20most%20popular%20design%20%E2%80%94%20the%20original%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noopener%20sponsored%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Flaneeight.com%2Fproduct%2Fmens-trainer-ad-1-cloud-white%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETrainer%20AD1%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EAmir's%20review%20of%20the%20Lane%20Eight%20Men's%20Trainer%20AD1%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20pair%20of%20feet%20wearing%20the%20Lane%20Eight%20Men's%20Trainer%20AD1%20in%20Cloud%20White.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F628e826c5a23e50018f6d663%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAmir%20wearing%20the%20Lane%20Eight%20Men's%20Trainer%20AD1%20in%20Cloud%20White.%3Cp%3EAmir%20Ismael%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Trainer%20AD1%20features%20a%20unique%20lacing%20system%20that%20spans%20the%20lateral%20and%20medial%20sides%20of%20the%20midfoot%2C%20rather%20than%20just%20at%20the%20top%20of%20the%20foot.%20The%20design%20really%20helped%20to%20keep%20my%20foot%20secure%20and%20locked%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20shoes%20are%20designed%20for%20all-around%20training%2C%20you%20won't%20find%20super%20bouncy%20midsoles%20and%20sculpted%20outsoles.%20The%20bottoms%20are%20mostly%20flat%2C%20which%20allowed%20me%20stay%20planted%20and%20balanced%20during%20workouts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20with%20the%20firm%20midsoles%20and%20flat%20bottoms%2C%20the%20shoes%20are%20made%20comfortable%20with%20algae-based%20beaded%20foam%20insoles.%20I've%20experienced%20similar%20technology%20in%20shoes%20from%20Adidas%20and%20Puma%2C%20and%20it%20works%20just%20as%20well%20on%20the%20Lane%20Eight%20Trainer%20AD%201.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3ESally's%20review%20of%20the%20Lane%20Eight%20Women's%20Trainer%20AD%201%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20pair%20of%20feet%20wearing%20the%20Lane%20Eight%20Women's%20Trainer%20AD1%20in%20Dusty%20Taupe.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F628e82a8ffc8350018eac3ee%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESally%20wearing%20the%20Lane%20Eight%20Women's%20Trainer%20AD1%20in%20Dusty%20Taupe.%3Cp%3ESally%20Kaplan%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI've%20worn%20my%20Lane%20Eight%20sneakers%20to%20the%20gym%20for%20several%20types%20of%20workouts%2C%20from%20cardio%20to%20strength%20training%2C%20and%20I've%20been%20loving%20the%20lightly%20cushy%20soles%20for%20treadmill%20or%20machine%20days.%20The%20little%20bumps%20on%20the%20insoles%20make%20wearing%20the%20shoes%20feel%20almost%20therapeutic%2C%20minus%20the%20usual%20geriatric%20aesthetic%20associated%20with%20features%20like%20that.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20shoes%20don't%20have%20a%20tongue%2C%20which%20is%20definitely%20a%20bonus%20for%20me.%20I%20find%20the%20sock-like%20fit%20to%20be%20snug%20but%20not%20too%20tight%2C%20and%20the%20toe%20gives%20me%20ample%20room%20to%20wiggle%20around%20and%20readjust%20without%20slipping%20or%20sliding.%20The%20arch%20support%20is%20decent%2C%20but%20not%20extreme%2C%20so%20you%20may%20need%20to%20put%20new%20insoles%20in%20if%20you%20require%20a%20lot%20of%20arch%20support.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20terms%20of%20design%2C%20I'm%20really%20into%20the%20taupe%2Fgum%20sole%20combo%20%E2%80%94%20they%20almost%20feel%20Yeezy-esque%20but%20without%20being%20overly%20trendy%2C%20so%20I%20can%20wear%20them%20for%20errands%20and%20on%20the%20weekend%20with%20sweatsuits%20and%20casual%20athleisure.%20%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%94%20Sally%20Kaplan%2C%20executive%20editor%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3ESizing%20and%20fit%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20am%20usually%20a%20size%208%20so%20that's%20what%20I%20ordered%2C%20and%20they%20fit%20true-to-size%20for%20me.%20My%20toes%20have%20enough%20room%20to%20move%20around%20at%20the%20top%20of%20the%20shoe%2C%20but%20they%20don't%20slip%20or%20slide.%20My%20high%20arches%20can%20cause%20sock-like%20shoes%20to%20feel%20a%20bit%20tight%20around%20the%20top%20of%20my%20foot%2C%20so%20that's%20the%20one%20drawback%20for%20me.%3Cstrong%3E%20%E2%80%94%20Sally%20Kaplan%2C%20executive%20editor%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI'm%20a%20true%20men's%20size%208%2C%20but%20I%20usually%20size%20up%20to%20an%208.5%20for%20sock-like%20sneakers.%20Even%20so%2C%20I%20experienced%20the%20same%20bit%20of%20tightness%20at%20the%20top%20of%20my%20foot%20that%20Sally%20mentioned.%20Although%20my%20toes%20have%20enough%20space%20in%20the%208.5%2C%20I%20think%20a%20size%209%20would%20have%20fit%20better.%20I%20have%20no%20doubt%20that%20your%20shoes%20will%20still%20fit%20well%20if%20you%20go%20up%20a%20full%20size.%20%E2%80%94%20%3Cstrong%3EAmir%20Ismael%2C%20senior%20reporter%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3ECons%20to%20consider%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMinor%20sizing%20issues%20aside%2C%20we%20both%20had%20really%20good%20experiences%20with%20Lane%20Eight%20sneakers.%20At%20%24130%2C%20they're%20more%20affordable%20than%20most%20performance%20sneakers.%20Although%20you%20can%20buy%20better%20shoes%20designed%20specifically%20for%20running%20or%20deadlifting%2C%20the%20versatility%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noopener%20sponsored%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Flaneeight.com%2Fproduct%2Fmens-trainer-ad-1-cloud-white%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETrainer%20AD%201%3C%2Fa%3E%20makes%20it%20well%20worth%20the%20price%20as%20a%20comfortable%20cross%20trainer%20that%20can%20handle%20several%20types%20of%20workouts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EThe%20bottom%20line%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELane%20Eight%20is%20carving%20its%20own%20lane%20in%20the%20footwear%20industry.%20While%20the%20use%20of%20sustainable%20materials%20isn't%20unique%20to%20the%20brand%20(it%20shouldn't%20be%20that%20way%20anyway)%2C%20Lane%20Eight's%20overall%20design%20and%20friendly%20approach%20to%20defining%20what%20it%20means%20to%20be%20an%20athlete%20are%20unique.%20The%20versatility%20of%20the%20Trainer%20AD1%20makes%20it%20the%20perfect%20entry-level%2C%20all-around%20workout%20and%20training%20sneaker%20for%20people%20who%20care%20about%20the%20planet.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fstyle%2Flane-eight-sneaker-review%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1776866929000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F628e81f9ffc8350018eac3b5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fstyle%2Flane-eight-sneaker-review%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22We%20tested%20the%20brand's%20most%20popular%20cross-trainers%20in%20and%20out%20of%20the%20gym%2C%20and%20you'd%20never%20know%20they're%20made%20from%20recycled%20bottles%20and%20algae.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22aismael%40businessinsider.com%20(Amir%20Ismael)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fstyle%2Flane-eight-sneaker-review%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22These%20Adidas%20sneakers%20were%20designed%20specifically%20to%20meet%20the%20demands%20of%20city%20runners%20%E2%80%94%20we%20put%20them%20to%20the%20test%20on%20the%20streets%20of%20NYC%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWhen%20you%20buy%20through%20our%20links%2C%20Business%20Insider%20may%20earn%20an%20affiliate%20commission.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finsider-reviews-expertise-in-product-reviews%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELearn%20more%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223197%5C%22%