tentially%20painful%20side%20effect%20of%20excessive%20sweat%20is%20thigh%20chafe.%20I%20swear%20by%20a%20few%20pairs%20of%20super-thin%2C%20non-compressive%2C%20%3Cstrong%3Eanti-thigh%20chafe%20shorties%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3B%20I've%20tried%20a%20bunch%2C%20and%20my%20absolute%20favorite%20version%20is%20this%20super-smooth%2C%20thin%20Knix%20pair%2C%20aptly%20named%20the%20Thigh%20Saver.%20They%20have%20a%20high%20waist%20but%20no%20compression%20so%20they%20don't%20have%20the%20awful%20sausage-casing%20feel.%20They're%20available%20in%20sizes%20up%20to%20a%203XL%20(equivalent%20to%20size%2024%20to%2026).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20also%20can't%20live%20without%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noopener%20sponsored%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-1511737761779-20%26h%3D7f62f185d81d46c0f3ad3ca4f1b67c63090a5cc212ee3b017736f96d9e7810eb%26postID%3D61b8efdbf2a36b1ac9f490ec%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fstyle%252Fhow-to-stay-cool-in-the-heat%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fclick.linksynergy.com%252Fdeeplink%253Fid%253DEHFxW6yx8Uo%2526amp%253Bmid%253D40468%2526amp%253Bmurl%253Dhttps%25253A%25252F%25252Fwww.bandier.com%25252Fproducts%25252Fthigh-rescue-stick-no-color%25253F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMegababe's%20Thigh%20Chafe%20stick%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20lightly%2C%20pleasantly%20scented%20anti-friction%20formula%20with%20moisturizing%20grapeseed%20oil%20and%20vitamin%20E%20in%20a%20deodorant-esque%20package.%20I'll%20use%20the%20Thigh%20Chafe%20stick%20in%20place%20of%20my%20trusty%20Knix%20shorts%20sometimes%2C%20like%20at%20the%20beach%20or%20pool%2C%20or%20just%20an%20insanely%20hot%20day%20when%20I%20can't%20bear%20to%20have%20any%20additional%20layers%20of%20clothing%20on%20beyond%20what's%20absolutely%20essential.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EUse%20a%20cooling%20towel%20for%20more%20than%20just%20your%20workouts.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221001%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sweaty%20weat