on%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EIt's%20time%20to%20put%20away%20your%20clunky%20boots%20and%20slip%20into%20a%20pair%20of%20sleek%20summer%20shoes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EA%20good%20summer%20shoe%20should%20be%20able%20to%20both%20keep%20your%20feet%20cool%20and%20dry%20and%20complete%20your%20outfit.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EFlip-flops%20don't%20have%20to%20be%20your%20go-to%20summer%20footwear.%20Here%20are%2019%20alternatives.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWarmer%20weather%20is%20here%2C%20and%20that%20means%20transitioning%20from%20heavy%20boots%20and%20chunky%20shoes%20to%20something%20sleek%2C%20cool%2C%20and%20beach-friendly%20that%20pairs%20well%20with%20your%20lighter%20wardrobe.%20Flip%20flops%20don't%20have%20to%20be%20your%20go-to%20summer%20footwear%20when%20there%20are%20boat%20shoes%2C%20slip-ons%2C%20sneakers%2C%20or%20even%20something%20more%20unusual%20like%20a%20clog.%20Live%20a%20little.%20We've%20gathered%20together%20the%20best%20of%20a%20range%20of%20styles%2C%20including%20several%20eco-friendly%20selections%20like%20a%20vegan%20sneaker%20made%20from%20cactus%20(yes%2C%20cactus)%2C%20so%20you%20can%20feel%20good%20while%20looking%20good%20this%20summer.%20These%20shoes%20are%20going%20to%20kick%20your%20summer%20look%20up%20to%20the%20next%20level%2C%20whether%20you're%20wearing%20a%20seersucker%20suit%20or%20shorts%20and%20a%20T.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJust%20note%20that%20while%20many%20of%20these%20styles%20are%20unisex%20and%20offer%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20sizing%2C%20others%20are%20geared%20towards%20men's%20sizing.%20For%20smaller%20sizes%20see%20our%20guide%20focused%20on%20women's%20summer%20shoes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3EHere%20are%20the%20best%20summer%20shoes%20for%20men%20in%202021%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EVans%20Classic%20Slip-Ons%20in%20Pink%20Lemonade%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221800%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Vans%20Classic%20Slip-Ons%20in%20Pink%20Lemonade%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%