s%20a%20leather%20liner%20and%20footbed%20for%20breathability%20and%20a%20Goodyear%20welted%20outsole%20for%20longevity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ECasca%20Avro%20Knit%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221800%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Casca%20Avro%20Knit%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F60c3ced623393a00188e2c97%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221350%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ECasca%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch3%3EThe%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcasca.com%2Fproducts%2Fmens-avro-ns%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECasca%20Avro%20Knit%3C%2Fa%3E%20may%20convince%20you%20to%20ditch%20your%20white%20leather%20sneakers%20this%20summer%20thanks%20to%20its%20minimalist%20aesthetic%20and%20are%20ultra%20comfortable%20and%20breathable.%C2%A0%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Caside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESizing%20options%3A%205.5%20to%2013.5.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EColor%20options%3A%208%20colorways%2C%20including%20a%20stunning%20Ash%20White.%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Faside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECasca's%20Avro%20Knit%20may%20convince%20you%20to%20ditch%20your%20white%20leather%20sneakers%20this%20summer.%20These%20shoes%20incorporate%20several%20innovations%2C%20like%20an%20internal%20%26quot%3Bcage%26quot%3B%20that%20helps%20the%20shoe%20maintain%20its%20shape%20and%20uppers%20made%20from%20a%20single%20panel%20of%20fabric%20making%20them%20seamless.%20These%20fit%20like%20a%20glove%20but%20are%20still%20ultra%20breathable.%20The%20Avro%20Knits%20have%20a%20super%20cushioned%20insole%2C%20micro-suede%20lining%2C%20and%C2%A0%20plush%20padding%20at%20the%20back%20of%20the%20collar..%20I%20prefer%20wearing%20these%20without%20socks%20but%20I%20did%20get%20a%20blister%20on%20my%20right%20pinky%20toe%20after%20walking%201.5%20miles%20when%20I%20first%20got%20them%2C%20so%20I%20recommend%20breaking%20them%20in%20with%20socks%20on.%20After%20a%20few%20wears%20they've%20become%20one%20of%20the%20most%20comfortable%20pairs%20of%20sneakers%20I%20own.%20Besides%20that%2C%20the%20Avro%20Knit%20is%20just%20a%20great-looking%20shoe.%20The%20Ash%20White%20is%20especially%20so%2C%20with%20its%20subtle%20monochromatic%20coloring.%20These%20are%20minimalist%20enough%20to%20pair%20with%20business%20casual%20or%20a%20summer%20suit.%20According%20to%20Braden%20Parker%2C%20Casca's%20CEO%20and%20Cofounder%2C%20the%20company%20takes%20the%20best%20technology%20from%20different%20footwear%20verticals%2C%20like%20running%20shoes%20and%20hiking%20boots%2C%20and%20incorporates%20them%20into%20timeless%20silhouettes%20that%20are%20meant%20to%20last%20for%20years.%20For%20example%2C%20their%20outsoles%20are%20made%20from%20the%20type%20of%20rubber%20found%20in%20the%20boots%20used%20by%20mountaineers%20to%20scale%20Mount%20Everest.%20For%20an%20extra%20%2465%20you%20can%20get%20SmartFit%203D%20custom%20insoles%20from%20the%20company%20that%20is%20as%20easy%20as%20downloading%20an%20app%20and%20scanning%20your%20feet%20with%20your%20smartphone.%20They%20do%20the%20rest.%20Casca%20also%20has%20a%20two-year%20warranty%20that%20covers%20all%20manufacturing%20defects.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ESperry%20Men's%20Gold%20Cup%20Authentic%20Original%202-Eye%20Soft%20Leather%20Boat%20Shoe%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221800%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sperry%20Men's%20Gold%20Cup%20Authentic%20Original%202-Eye%20Soft%20Leather%20Boat%20Shoe%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F60c7549e23393a00188e2e58%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221350%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ESperry%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noopener%20sponsored%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiauto-59161-20%26h%3D6dcf075789a4383c4577645b6675be61a69103424deed134fdace487e74c5da3%26postID%3D61b8efdbf2a36b1ac9f493df%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fstyle%252F