tion%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch3%3EYou%20wouldn't%20know%20it%20by%20seeing%20or%20even%20touching%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.clae.com%2Fpages%2Fbradley-cactus-leather%23r-1604568952364%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EClae%20Bradley%20Cactus%20sneakers%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20they're%20not%20made%20out%20of%20animal%20leather%2C%20but%20an%20innovative%20and%20sustainable%20cactus%20material.%20Better%20yet%2C%20they're%20stylish%20and%20extremely%20comfortable.%C2%A0%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Caside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESizing%20options%3A%204%20to%2014.%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EColor%20options%3A%20Black%2C%20white%2C%20and%20green.%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Faside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYou%20wouldn't%20know%20it%20by%20looking%20at%20these%20sneakers%20or%20even%20touching%20them%20that%20they%20aren't%20made%20out%20of%20animal%20leather%20but%20cactus.%20Yes%2C%20cactus!%20Clae's%20Bradley%20Cactus%20sneakers%20are%20the%20first%20on%20the%20market%20to%20be%20made%20using%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rockport.com%2Fdunham%2Fmens-captain-boat-shoe%2FMCN410.html%3Fdwvar_MCN410_color%3DNAVY%2520BLACK%26cgid%3Ddunham-mens%23start%3D1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDesserto%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20an%20award-winning%20sustainable%20leather%20made%20from%20mature%20nopal%20leaves%20and%20involving%20a%20patented%20process%20from%20the%20Mexican%20company%20Adriano%20Di%20Marti.%20Clae%2C%20based%20in%20Los%20Angeles%2C%20has%20been%20an%20independent%20eco-conscious%20footwear%20brand%20for%20two%20decades%20and%20has%20continued%20to%20push%20the%20boundaries%20of%20sustainable%20style%20with%20shoes%20that%20are%20timeless%2C%20well-made%2C%20and%20appropriately%20priced.%20The%20Bradley%20Cactus%20is%20no%20exception.%20It's%20a%20minimalist%20sneaker%20that%20is%20as%20comfortable%20as%20it%20is%20good-looking.%20It%20features%20a%20natural%20rubber%20outsole%20that%20contrasts%20nicely%20with%20the%20color%20of%20the%20uppers%2C%20particularly%20with%20the%20green%20colorway%2C%20but%20with%20the%20white%20and%20black%20colorways%20as%20well.%20The%20first%20day%20I%20had%20them%20I%20walked%20five%20miles%20with%20no%20foot%20issues.%20They%20have%20molded%20EVA%20footbeds%20and%20neoprene%20heel%20accents%20that%20help%20make%20these%20sneakers%20so%20comfortable.%20I%20also%20found%20them%20as%20breathable%20as%20animal%20leather%20in%20hot%20weather.%20They%20also%20feature%20two%20vents%20on%20the%20instep%20that%20help%20circulate%20air.%20The%20Bradley%20Cactus%20is%20an%20innovative%20shoe%20that's%20stylish%2C%20sustainable%2C%20and%20reasonably%20priced%20at%20%24150.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ENisolo%20Alejandro%20Woven%20Slip%20On%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221800%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Nisolo%20Alejandro%20Woven%20Slip%20On%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F60c759b36d855e0018157cb5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221350%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ENisolo%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch3%3EUpgrade%20from%20your%20everyday%20sandals%20to%20Nisolo's%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noopener%20sponsored%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiauto-59161-20%26h%3Dfdc3142fa9a38f7d50a5cd57486ce7eb0862115fe599973013582fc979ce64d1%26postID%3D61b8efdbf2a36b1ac9f493df%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fstyle%252Fbest-mens-summer-shoes%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fnisolo.uvwgb9.net%252Fc%252F196318%252F698455%252F10656%253Fu%253Dhttps%25253A%25252F%25252Fnisolo.com%25252Fcollections%25252Fsandals-and-slip-ons%25252Fproducts%25252Fmens-leather-slip-on-woven-black%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAlejandro%20Woven%20Slip%20On%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20features%20hand-woven%20leather%20uppers%20and%20high%20ethical%20and%20environmental%20production%20standards%20as%20well.%C2%A0%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Caside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESizing%20options%3A%208%20to%2013.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EColor%20options%3A%20brown%20and%20black.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Faside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENisolo%2C%20a%20Nashville-based%20footwear%20company%20that%20mainly%20produces%20its%20shoes%20at%20its%20own%20facility%20in%20Peru%2C%20has%20an%20elegant%20take%20on%20the%20summer%20slip-on%20that's%20an%20upgrade%20from%20your%20everyday%20sandal.%20The%20Alejandro%20Woven%20Slip%20On%20is%20made%20from%20handwoven%20leather%20that's%20water%20resistant%2C%20making%20it%20perfect%20for%20beach%20days%20and%20poolside.%20The%20woven%20technique%20used%20in%20the%20uppers%20provides%20breathability%20in%20the%20heart%20of%20summer%20and%20the%20cushioned%20insoles%20make%20them%20perfect%20for%20all-day%20wear.%20They're%20also%20partially%20lined%20with%20a%20soft%20leather%20for%20added%20comfort.%20The%20outsoles%20are%20made%20of%20leather%20and%20have%20a%20slip-resistant%20rubber%20heel%20cap.%20Besides%20looking%20great%2C%20you%20can%20feel%20good%20about%20them%20as%20well.%20The%20leather%20is%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.leatherworkinggroup.com%2Fwho-we-are%2Fabout-us%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecertified%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20meeting%20high%20environmental%20standards%20for%20its%20production%20and%20Nisolo%20is%20a%20Certified%20B%20Corporation%20that%20meets%20high%20ethical%20standards%20like%20providing%20a%20living%20wage%20to%20its%20workers%20and%20being%200%25%20Net%20Carbon.%20I%20found%20that%20there%20was%20a%20short%20break-in%20period%20of%20a%20few%20wears%2C%20but%20the%20shoes%20soon%20conformed%20to%20my%20feet%20and%20became%20quite%20comfortable.%20The%20Alejandro%20Woven%20Slip%20On%20pairs%20well%20with%20shorts%20or%20light%20pants%20(linen%2C%20summer-weight%20chinos%2C%20or%20seersucker)%20with%20the%20pant%20legs%20rolled%20up%2