r%20shorts%20and%20a%20T-shirt%E2%80%94and%20defy%20the%20whims%20of%20fashion.%20There%20are%20several%20subcategories%2C%20including%20the%20Penny%20Loafer%2C%20which%20is%20differentiated%20by%20the%20decorative%20leather%20strip%20across%20the%20vamp%20with%20a%20lip-like%20cutout%20that%20is%20the%20perfect%20size%20to%20store%20a%20penny%20(probably%20more%20useful%20back%20when%20you%20could%20actually%20buy%20something%20for%20a%20penny).%20The%20G.H.%20Bass%20%26amp%3B%20Co.%20Larson%20Nubuck%20Weejuns%20are%20a%20classic%2C%20literally.%20They've%20been%20a%20signature%20style%20since%201936%20when%20the%20company%20popularized%20loafers%20in%20the%20U.S.%20The%20uppers%20are%20a%20soft%20nubuck%20leather%20featuring%20classic%20moc%20stitching%20and%20%26quot%3Bbeefroll%26quot%3B%20detailing%20where%20the%20penny%20keeper%20is%20stitched%20onto%20the%20shoe%2C%20a%20soft%20synthetic%20lining%2C%20and%20a%20chunky%20leather%20outsole.%20Hand%20sewn%20in%20El%20Salvador%2C%20these%20loafers%20are%20sharp%2C%20comfortable%2C%20and%20will%20smarten%20up%20any%20outfit%20you%20pair%20them%20with.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EKizik%20Madrid%20Eco%20Knit%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221800%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Kizik%20Madrid%20Eco%20Knit%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F60c75e7823393a00188e2e84%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221350%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EKizik%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch3%3EKizik's%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fkizik.com%2Fcollections%2Fmens-new%2Fproducts%2Fmens-madrid-eco-knit-light-grey-grey-outsole%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMadrid%20Eco%20Knit%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20extremely%20comfortable%2C%20easy%20to%20get%20in%20and%20out%20of%2C%20and%20will%20keep%20your%20feet%20cool%20in%20the%20heart%20of%20the%20summer.%C2%A0%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Caside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESizing%20options%3A%204.5%20to%2015%2C%20standard%20a