Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20local%20brews%20and%20casual%20eats%20at%20Brickyard%20Hollow%20Brewing%20Company%20to%20Mediterranean%20cuisine%20at%20The%20Front%20Yard%2C%20there's%20something%20for%20every%20palate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20late-night%20eats%2C%20make%20your%20way%20up%20the%20lighted%20stairs%20to%20a%20treehouse%20oasis%20for%20chips%20and%20queso%20and%20a%20fresh%20margarita%20at%20Treehouse%20Taqueria.%20Then%2C%20follow%20the%20piano%20tunes%20down%20the%20street%20to%20The%20Front%20Porch%20Piano%20Bar%20%26amp%3B%20Restaurant%20for%20a%20sing-along.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20must-try%20is%20CREW%20Ogunquit%2C%20a%20restaurant%20and%20bar%20with%20live%20music.%20If%20you%20plan%20your%20trip%20for%20early%20June%2C%20you%20can%20even%20enjoy%20the%20restaurant's%20rainbow%20menu%20of%20Pride%20Month%20cocktails.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226ff44f54-a146-4cb0-be3e-195b592ee523%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EOther%20coastal%20Maine%20towns%20are%20within%20short%20driving%20distance%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22916%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20expanse%20of%20blue%20water%20and%20some%20houses%20in%20Kennebunkport%2C%20Maine.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69dfb467777ecc79d62f4f3d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22654%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EKennebunkport%20is%20a%20quick%20drive%20away.%3Cp%3EMorgan%20Rizzo%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20looking%20for%20even%20more%20Maine%20charm%2C%20there%20are%20other%20cute%20towns%20that%20are%20easy%20to%20visit%20from%20Ogunquit.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffavorite-us-small-towns-from-frequent-traveler-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EKennebunkport%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20dreamy%20destination%20filled%20with%20boats%20dotting%20the%20harbor%20and%20nautical%20shops%2C%20is%20less%20than%20a%2030-minute%20drive%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20your%20way%20there%2C%20st