eparture.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EI'm%20glad%20we%20didn't%20visit%20beforehand%2C%20as%20it%20made%20it%20easier%20to%20make%20decisions%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fquit-job-move-barcelona-commute-to-london-cheaper-affordable-visa-2026-1%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecommit%20to%20the%20move%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20day%20my%20family%20arrived%20at%20our%20new%20flat%20in%20Spain%2C%20I%20felt%20a%20wave%20of%20panic.%20As%20I%20was%20lying%20down%20on%20a%20bare%20mattress%20in%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffurniture-free-living-benefits-lifestyle-health-minimalist-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eunfurnished%20apartment%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20reality%20of%20having%20just%20moved%20to%20a%20country%20none%20of%20us%20had%20ever%20visited%20before%20finally%20hit%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20have%20I%20done%3F%26quot%3B%20I%20wondered.%20I%20kept%20my%20anxieties%20to%20myself%2C%20not%20wanting%20to%20worry%20my%20husband%20and%20two%20young%20sons.%20We%20were%20all%20exhausted%2C%20disoriented%2C%20and%20surrounded%20by%20luggage%20containing%20the%20items%20we'd%20brought%20from%20Connecticut.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENeedless%20to%20say%2C%20we%20had%20enough%20on%20our%20plates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20I%20closed%20my%20eyes%20and%20trusted%20that%20the%20feelings%20passed.%20Little%20did%20I%20know%2C%20moving%20to%20an%20unfamiliar%20country%20would%20usher%20us%20into%20a%20life-changing%20adventure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223524295b-add0-45bd-aca6-0b4c79700f60%5C%22%3ESpain%20appealed%20to%20me%20even%20without%20on-the-ground%20experience%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Rebecca%20Cretella%20and%20her%20husband%20in%20Spain%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69e0e46e557731f181e9549b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20first%20few%20months%20living%20abroad%20were%20lonely%2C%20as%20we%20arrived%20without%20an%20established%20network.%3Cp%3ERebecca%20Cretella%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20husband%20and%20I%20were%20on%20the%20same%20page%20about%20our%20desire%20to%20leave%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20wanted%20a%20different%20childhood%20for%20our%20kids%2C%20who%20were%2010%20and%206%20at%20the%20time%20of%20the%20move%2C%20and%20more%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftime-to-rethink-what-work-life-balance-really-means-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ework-life%20balance%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20ourselves.%20After%20considering%20several%20countries%20(including%20Portugal%20and%20Italy)%2C%20Spain%20won%20us%20over.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20felt%20a%20personal%20pull%20to%20the%20country%20that%20I%20still%20can't%20fully%20explain.%20Since%20we%20didn't%20have%20the%20time%20or%20money%20to%20go%20on%20scouting%20trips%2C%20we%20researched%20cities%20and%20towns%20obsessively%20before%20committing%20to%20Madrid%20as%20our%20landing%20pad.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20it%20didn't%20feel%20right%2C%20we%20figured%20we%20could%20always%20change%20course%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELooking%20back%2C%20choosing%20Madrid%20simplified%20everything.%20We%20didn't%20second-guess%20our%20choice%20or%20ponder%20whether%20somewhere%20else%20might've%20been%20better.%20Once%20we%20made%20a%20decision%2C%20we%20were%20fully%20committed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c7eb7f87-92cf-4519-8ab1-cf7044dd58b0%5C%22%3EWe%20relied%20on%20research%2C%20relocation%20agencies%2C%20and%20advanced%20planning%20before%20the%20move%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20we%20couldn't%20visit%20Madrid%2C%20we%20did%20a%20lot%20of%20research%20from%20our%20home%20in%20Connecticut%20before%20the%20move.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20went%20down%20Google%20rabbit%20holes%2C%20watched%20YouTube%20videos%20about%20Spain%2C%20read%20books%20about%20moving%20abroad%2C%20joined%20Facebook%20groups%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoved-abroad-relationship-with-parents-changed-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Epeople%20relocating%20overseas%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20used%20social%20media%20to%20follow%20families%20that%20had%20already%20made%20similar%20moves.%20We%20also%20worked%20with%20an%20immigration%20lawyer%20to%20help%20us%20navigate%20the%20visa-application%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20best%20decisions%20we%20made%20was%20hiring%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-move-abroad-expat-2016-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Erelocation%20agency%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20help%20us%20find%20housing.%20Selling%20our%20house%20in%20Connecticut%20and%20getting%20rid%20of%20most%20of%20our%20belongings%20already%20overwhelmed%20me%2C%20so%20navigating%20rentals%20in%20a%20foreign%20country%20where%20we%20didn't%20speak%20the%20language%20would've%20pushed%20me%20over%20the%20edge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20relocation%20agency%20secured%20us%20a%20flat%20in%20Las%20Rozas%20de%20Madrid%2C%20a%20suburb%20outside%20the%20capital%20city%2C%20that%20was%20well-situated%20between%20our%20children's%20school%20and%20my%20husband's%20university.%20The%20area%20also%20has%20great%20public%20transportation%2C%20which%20was%20important%20since%20we%20don't%20have%20a%20car%20in%20Spain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20husband%20and%20I%20used%20the%20International%20Schools%20Database%20to%20choose%20one%20for%20our%20sons.%20Once%20we%20selected%20a%20school%2C%20we%20scheduled%20calls%20with%20directors%2C%20took%20virtual%20tours%2C%20and%20had%20our%20kids%20meet%20their%20principal%20and%20teachers%20over%20Zoom%20before%20we%20ever%20left%20Connecticut.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20the%20time%20we%20got%20on%20the%20plane%2C%20Spain%20didn't%20feel%20completely%20unknown.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225df250a3-40a2-4bdc-b35b-4f16597dcd30%5C%22%3EStill%2C%20nothing%20fully%20prepared%20us%20for%20our%20arrival%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Rebecca%20Cretella%20and%20her%20sons%20in%20Spain%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69e0e45b557731f181e95499%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWe%20live%20in%20a%20suburb%20outside%20of%20Madrid%20that's%20mostly%20walkable.%3Cp%3ERebecca%20Cretella%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20remember%20seeing%20Spain%20for%20the%20first%20time%20on%20the%20drive%20into%20Madrid.%20It%20looked%20so%20different%20from%20Connecticut%2C%20and%20I%20kept%20thinking%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20my%20home%20now.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20van%20dropped%20us%20off%20at%20a%20small%20real-estate%20office%20to%20meet%20our%20landlords%20and%20pick%20up%20the%20keys.%20Our%20landlords%20helped%20us%20carry%20our%20suitcases%20to%20the%20apartment%20before%20treating%20us%20to%20lunch.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20we%20realized%20we%20didn't%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fways-to-get-more-from-household-basics-2015-7%23lemons-freshen-up-your-home-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebasic%20household%20items%3C%2Fa%3E%20(think%3A%20toilet%20paper%2C%20cookware%2C%20towels%2C%20and%20a%20trash%20can)%2C%20they%20drove%20us%20to%20a%20nearby%20mall%20and%20helped%20us%20buy%20everything%20we%20needed%2C%20making%20multiple%20trips%20to%20transport%20it%20all%20back%20to%20our%20flat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHours%20after%20arriving%20in%20a%20country%20where%20we%20knew%20no%20one%2C%20strangers%20had%20already%20shown%20us%20kindness%20I'll%20never%20forget.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2281013f67-0964-4a79-9b8e-986ac7e0ca45%5C%22%3EAlthough%20we're%20still%20getting%20to%20know%20Spain%2C%20we%20already%20feel%20a%20sense%20of%20belonging%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Rebecca%20Cretella%20and%20her%20family%20in%20Spain%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69e0e4af3c23517615b2fb66%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMy%20family%20relocated%20from%20the%20US%20to%20Spain%20in%202025.%3Cp%3ERebecca%20Cretella%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EVisiting%20a%20place%20before%20moving%20there%20can%2C%20of%20course%2C%20be%20useful%2C%20but%20it's%20not%20the%20only%20path.%20And%20in%20some%20cases%2C%20it%20can%20complicate%20decisions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20I'd%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftravel-to-spain-months-with-toddlers-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Escouted%20out%20Spain%3C%2Fa%3E%20before%20relocating%2C%20I%20might've%20second-guessed%20our%20choice%20or%20struggled%20to%20commit%20to%20one%20place.%20It%20might've%20opened%20up%20too%20many%20options%2C%20making%20the%20decision%20feel%20more%20scary%2C%20more%20%3Cem%3Ereal%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20did%20enough%20research%20in%20the%20US%20to%20make%20a%20thoughtful%20decision.%20And%20when%20the%20time%20to%20board%20the%20plane%20came%2C%20we%20trusted%20our%20guts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlmost%20a%20year%20in%2C%20Spain%20has%20already%20started%20to%20feel%20like%20home.%20Our%20neighborhood%20feels%20like%20ours.%20We%20know%20all%20the%20bus%20drivers.%20Caf%C3%A9%20owners%20give%20us%20a%20friendly%20nod.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20I'm%20still%20working%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-make-friends-as-an-adult-living-abroad-home-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebuilding%20a%20community%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I%20never%20expected%20to%20feel%20so%20comfortable%20less%20than%20a%20year%20after%20moving.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20some%20ways%2C%20not%20visiting%20Spain%20ahead%20of%20time%20helped%20my%20family.%20We%20didn't%20have%20a%20version%20or%20concrete%20idea%20of%20Spain%20to%20compare%20our%20life%20to.%20Once%20we%20made%20our%20decision%2C%20we%20grew%20into%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20art