re%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20don%E2%80%99t%20just%20plant%20and%20walk%20away%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Vishal.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20map%20each%20site%20using%20KML%20Polygons%20%E2%80%94%20satellite-based%20tools%20that%20log%20the%20exact%20coordinates%20of%20every%20mini%20forest.%20This%20lets%20us%20maintain%20a%20digital%20record%2C%20verify%20locations%2C%20and%20track%20growth.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20forests%20are%20feeding%20families%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20project%E2%80%99s%20social%20impact%20matches%20its%20ecological%20gains.%20Beyond%20trees%2C%20it%20has%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F418054%2Fneeti-goel-restaurateur-mumbai-khaanachiye-lb-trust-sundarbans-tiger-widows%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebecome%20a%20source%20of%20livelihood%20for%20thousands%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20rural%20Punjab.%20Around%20120%20people%20work%20at%20its%20nurseries%2C%20and%20the%20initiative%20collaborates%20with%20the%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20National%20Rural%20Employment%20Guarantee%20Act%20(MGNREGA)%20to%20scale%20up%20plantations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20the%20end%20of%202024%2C%20TBTP%20had%20generated%20more%20than%2015%2C000%20jobs%20through%20MGNREGA%2C%20most%20filled%20by%20women%20and%20young%20people.%20These%20roles%20extend%20beyond%20wages%2C%20involving%20environmental%20custodianship%20from%20land%20preparation%20to%20sapling%20care.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMGNREGA%20has%20been%20instrumental%20in%20bringing%20in%20local%20workers%20who%20not%20only%20earn%20but%20also%20develop%20a%20sense%20of%20responsibility%20towards%20the%20land.%20When%20someone%20helps%20raise%20a%20forest%20from%20scratch%2C%20it%20becomes%20personal%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Vishal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20watched%20young%20people%20grow%20into%20community%20leaders%20through%20this%20work.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20educate%20their%20neighbours%2C%20advocate%20for%20conservation%2C%20and%20carry%20the%20torch%20forward%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20sun%20sets%20over%20Rajinder%20Nagar%2C%20Inderjit%20walks%20slowly%20through%20his%20forest.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20the%20Punjab%20I%20remember%20as%20a%20child%20%E2%80%94%20lush%2C%20vibrant%2C%20alive.%20It%20is%20coming%20back%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%20In%20Lang%2C%20Romanpreet%20watches%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F493007%2Fbutterfly-friendly-plants-for-indian-homes-marigold-hibiscus-tulsi%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebutterflies%20flit%20through%20the%20branches%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-09-04T201626.909_11zon-1756997217.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Billion%20Tree%20Project%20helps%20to%20plant%20trees%20and%20is%20a%20consistent%20source%20of%20livelihood%20for%20many%20villagers%2C%20especially%20women%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-09-04T201626.909_11zon-1756997217.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-09-04T201626.909_11zon-1756997217-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-09-04T201626.909_11zon-1756997217-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-09-04T201626.909_11zon-1756997217-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-med