in%20flood%20affected%20Punjab%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fpunjab-floods-5-1757074126.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fpunjab-floods-5-1757074126-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fpunjab-floods-5-1757074126-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fpunjab-floods-5-1757074126-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fpunjab-floods-5-1757074126-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-496955%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EBotas%20are%20being%20deployed%20to%20perform%20rescue%20operations%20in%20flood-affected%20Punjab%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20has%20taken%20cognisance%20of%20the%20scale%20of%20the%20disaster%20and%20deployed%20the%20NDRF%2C%20SDRF%2C%20Army%2C%20Air%20Force%2C%20BSF%2C%20and%20police.%20Evacuations%20and%20food%20drops%20are%20being%20supported%20by%20helicopters.%20There%20have%20been%20438%20rapid%20response%20teams%2C%20360%20mobile%20medical%20units%2C%20and%20172%20ambulances%20dispatched%20statewide.%20Boats%20are%20being%20deployed%20in%20remote%20areas%20like%20Gurdaspur%20to%20reach%20isolated%20populations%2C%20including%20pregnant%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98My%20house%20is%20flooded%2C%20but%20I%20must%20give%20you%20something%20to%20eat%E2%80%99%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20only%20things%20that%20has%20kept%20Harmeet%20and%20his%20team%2C%20and%20the%20numerous%20other%20teams%20supported%20by%20Donatekart%2C%20going%20during%20this%20time%20has%20been%20the%20resilience%20they%20have%20seen%20among%20the%20people.%20%E2%80%9CWhile%20performing%20the%20rescues%2C%20when%20we%20go%20to%20their%20homes%2C%20which%20are%20completely%20flooded%2C%20they%20still%20say%2C%20%E2%80%9CMy%20kitchen%20is%20flooded%2C%20but%20can%20I%20offer%20you%20some%20milk%3F%20You%20have%20come%20to%20my%20house%2C%20and%20I%20should%20give%20you%20something.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fpunjab-floods-4-1757073764.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22There%20have%20been%20438%20rapid%20response%20teams%2C%20360%20mobile%20medical%20units%2C%20and%20172%20ambulances%20dispatched%20statewide%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fpunjab-floods-4-1757073764.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fpunjab-floods-4-1757073764-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fpunjab-floods-4-1757073764-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fpunjab-floods-4-1757073764-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fpunjab-floods-4-1757073764-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-496951%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThere%20have%20been%20438%20rapid%20response%20teams%2C%20360%20mobile%20medical%20units%2C%20and%20172%20ambulances%20dispatched%20statewide%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20tells%20another%20story%20of%20a%20rescue%20where%20a%20little%20girl%20began%20crying%20as%20she%2C%20along%20with%20her%20family%2C%20was%20taken%20away%20to%20the%20relief%20camp%20in%20the%20rescue%20boat.%20She%20watched%20her%20house%2C%20the%20one%20that%20her%20father%20had%20taken%20a%20loan%20for%20and%20put%20his%20life%20savings%20into%20building%2C%20crumble%20to%20pieces%2C%20washed%20away%20brick%20by%20brick.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20her%20father%20consoled%20her%2C%20%E2%80%98Houses%20can%20be%20rebuilt.%20At%20least%20we%20are%20alive.%E2%80%99%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F348884%2Fsenior-citizens-healthcare-boat-clinic-in-sundarbans-shis-foundation-abdul-wohab-sabitri-pal%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThese%20stories%20reveal%20the%20unbreakable%20spirit%20of%20the%20people%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Harmeet%20points%20out.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20it%E2%80%99s%20going%20to%20take%20a%20great%20deal%20of%20time%20for%20the%20farmers%20to%20tide%20through%20the%20losses.%20%E2%80%9CTheir%20animals%20are%20drowning%20and%20dying%3B%20this%20is%20leading%20to%20an%20increase%20in%20infections.%20We%20have%20our%20doctors%20across%20medical%20centres%20and%20relief%20camps%2C%20but%20the%20number%20of%20cases%20of%20waterborne%20diseases%2C%20skin%20infections%2C%20and%20diseases%20caused%20by%20mosquito%20bites%20is%20on%20the%20rise.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20the%20scale%20of%20the%20losses%2C%20he%20says%20they%20will%20only%20be%20able%20to%20assess%20this%20once%20the%20flood%20waters%20ebb.%20However%2C%20the%20distress%20will%20continue%20for%20farmers%20like%20Mohan%20who%20do%20not%20have%20a%20home%20to%20go%20back%20to.%20It%20isn%E2%80%99t%20just%20the%20present%20that%20keeps%20him%20up%20at%20night%2C%20but%20the%20uncertain%20future.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20your%20donation%20can%20help%20bring%20comfort%20today%20and%20strength%20tomorrow%20%E2%80%94%20for%20Mohan%2C%20and%20for%20countless%20others%20like%20him.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.donatekart.com%2FDisaster-Relief%2FThe-Better-India%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EDonate%20here.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3